import React from "react"; import "../index.css"; const Tour = () => { return (

ROAD HAUS

Starting at: $89,500 Unique architectural features with value engineering bring a high-quality tiny home at an affordable price. Turnkey and ready to be hooked up to any utility system, the RoadHaus Wedge is a great option for an alternative living lifestyle or home office.

JUPE

Starting at: $17,000 Jupe is a dwelling unit inspired by the stars, designed for new frontiers beyond the city and off the grid. It isn’t just a quick place to stay. It’s a gateway to the outside world.

UTOPIA

Starting at: $90,000 A creative roofline makes this home impressive even before setting foot inside. A large glass floor to ceiling window and a beautiful rounded staircase make this home unique and comfortable.

LUNA

Starting at: $75,000 Luna is a budget-conscious, high design tiny house. Surround yourself in nature and soak in the sun from nearly every view in your home thanks to Luna's gorgeous floor-to-ceiling glass.

INTREPID

Starting at: $90,000 A dynamic roofline, large opening glass doors, and lovely interior finishes inside set the Intrepid apart. You’ll find all the necessary amenities to live or travel in peace in this stylish tiny home.

NOYER

Starting at: $87,000 With only a limited amount of space, tiny homes begin to look rather similar. But not the Noyer. It’s entirely unique and designed to handle weather from sunny California to freezing temperatures in Quebec, this tiny home has been engineered and designed to handle anything you throw at it.

); } export default Tour;
